Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,==================== Part A ====================
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.33,0:01:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,宇宙万花筒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.01,0:01:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,吉特团提供的Yggdrasil（世界树）一旦投入实战
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.73,0:01:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,亚美利亚的残存兵力
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.94,0:02:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,可以轻易歼灭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.24,0:02:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,其中最大的功臣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.71,0:02:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,玛尼·安巴萨 全仗你的努力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.36,0:02:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,这么说过奖了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.43,0:02:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,感谢你不在的这段时间
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.75,0:02:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好好珍惜我的恭维
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.43,0:02:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,告辞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.91,0:02:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,卡巴迦里是昆达拉守护神的名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.43,0:02:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.45,0:02:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,是昆达拉的灵魂安息地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.72,0:02:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,卡巴的守护神
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.43,0:02:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,正确称呼是迦里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.76,0:02:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,和这架机体很配
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.09,0:02:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,吉特团真是多产呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.49,0:02:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,昆和契卡拉什么都往船上塞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.18,0:02:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,来地球一路没闲过
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.92,0:02:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,为维护？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.83,0:02:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,从组装开始！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.83,0:02:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,哇…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.23,0:02:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yggdrasil出击
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.26,0:02:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,多简洁的外形
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.42,0:03:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,上尉 你确认…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.42,0:03:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,要用Bifron做靶机吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.82,0:03:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,它已经接近极限了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.07,0:03:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,让驾驶员亲手了结
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.63,0:03:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.82,0:03:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,这里的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.36,0:03:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,似乎都很向往军队
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.00,0:03:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你们见过金星殖民圈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.68,0:03:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,过分和平就会产生那种人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.95,0:03:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,上尉 戴面具的时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.86,0:03:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我因为有玛尼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.55,0:03:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,才有了战斗的勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.58,0:03:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,这次玛尼失踪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.60,0:03:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我深深体会到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.79,0:03:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.51,0:03:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,愿意听听我的愿望吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.59,0:03:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 当然
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.93,0:03:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.46,0:03:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,和贝鲁利做朋友！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.92,0:03:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,这不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.32,0:03:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,他是个仰仗母亲家世
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.65,0:03:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,注定迈上仕途的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.64,0:03:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,这是误会
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.90,0:03:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,结识亚美利亚监军的女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.88,0:03:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,他迟早会成为独裁者！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.88,0:04:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,艾达和贝鲁利是姐弟！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.89,0:04:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你在说笑？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.76,0:04:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,他们出生于托瓦萨格的雷哈顿家族
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.20,0:04:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,婴儿的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.46,0:04:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,就被安排逃亡地球
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.63,0:04:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.63,0:04:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,能驾驶G-Self 是最好的证明
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.51,0:04:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,那如果是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.19,0:04:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,岂不是更纯正的贵族血统？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.31,0:04:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,天生被人吃的昆达拉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.81,0:04:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,在那些人看来连虫子也不如！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.80,0:04:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,导向护罩 良好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.76,0:04:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Bifron会如何进攻？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.55,0:04:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,不用管这些
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.89,0:04:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.67,0:04:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不愧是芭拉拉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.34,0:04:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,说到做到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.55,0:04:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,碎片？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.57,0:04:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,芭拉拉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.45,0:04:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,芭拉拉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.71,0:04:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,芭拉拉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.04,0:05:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,芭拉拉！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.95,0:05:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,芭拉拉！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.82,0:05:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,到底什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.36,0:05:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不是在胡闹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.21,0:05:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,是测试机动
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.66,0:05:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,没想到它这么机敏吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.55,0:05:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,确实 刚才的动作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.36,0:05:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,看外形绝无法想到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.82,0:05:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yggdrasil按预定时间出击
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.33,0:05:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,是 请吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.67,0:05:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我们到过的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.49,0:05:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,只是罗萨里奥Ⅹ和海桌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.53,0:05:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,不及金星殖民圈的1%
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.93,0:05:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,金星殖民圈的拉古总裁呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.23,0:05:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,他穿着奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.20,0:05:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,总是抱歉 抱歉的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.95,0:05:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.88,0:05:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,是位谦虚的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.48,0:05:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,200岁…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.74,0:05:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,第二站点Hayyan上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.78,0:05:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,母亲和昆珀上校在等您
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.62,0:06:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.74,0:06:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,亚美利亚舰队几时走的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.68,0:06:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,父亲说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.39,0:06:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,发给德瑞特舰队的停战协议迟迟得不到回音
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.10,0:06:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,所以出发 去催促他们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.78,0:06:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,从圣波尔图
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.27,0:06:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,一路打到低轨道的两支舰队
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.29,0:06:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,真的可能停战吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.81,0:06:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,如果归还神轿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.85,0:06:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,并非不能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.14,0:06:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,失礼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.35,0:06:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,神轿身上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.84,0:06:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,有这种力量
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.43,0:06:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,看重这些的时代
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.67,0:06:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,已经成为过去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.52,0:06:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,拉古总裁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.97,0:06:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,曾这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.26,0:06:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,害怕宇宙脐带教和禁忌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.43,0:06:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,会被人淡忘
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.76,0:06:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,二位的父母 曾忧心忡忡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.29,0:06:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,您认识他们？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.80,0:06:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.86,0:06:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,只是在圣波尔图听到类似传闻
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.54,0:06:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.03,0:06:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我们先告辞了 法皇大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.48,0:06:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.20,0:06:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我相信
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.24,0:06:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,在那个家庭长大是我的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.21,0:06:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,告辞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.84,0:06:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,一路顺风
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.97,0:07:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,贵安
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.89,0:07:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,贵安
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.15,0:07:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,贵安
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.91,0:07:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,法皇的小艇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.54,0:07:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,是去Hayyan吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.39,0:07:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我们也该出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.19,0:07:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.01,0:07:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,这可是难得的宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.08,0:07:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Dharma和Dahack
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.27,0:07:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Dharma和Dahack？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.70,0:07:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,瞧 就是它
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.55,0:07:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,以Dharma为装甲的机动战士？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.02,0:07:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,是吉特团那伙人的得意之作
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.53,0:07:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.65,0:07:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,那架Trinity
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.62,0:07:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,给碍事的手脚装上了武器
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.55,0:07:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,说是给我用
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.89,0:07:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,想马上试驾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.99,0:07:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,当然越早越好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.37,0:07:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,公主殿下？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.05,0:07:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,这就准备
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.53,0:07:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.49,0:07:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,听说你们接回了法皇大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.19,0:07:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,克里姆 感谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.08,0:08:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,公主殿下高兴就好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.62,0:08:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,有昨日火蝾螈的行动
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.47,0:08:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我们才能
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.33,0:08:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,把法皇大人顺利接回Capital塔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.02,0:08:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.10,0:08:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,这东西看起来真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.10,0:08:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Gehennam和Hecate
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.89,0:08:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,连续征战劳损严重
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.04,0:08:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,没带慰劳品的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.56,0:08:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,会恨你一辈子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.51,0:08:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.36,0:08:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,米克·杰克
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.64,0:08:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,克里姆·尼克也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.07,0:08:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我的任性给二位添了麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.16,0:08:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.49,0:08:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,弦月船带回的土特产…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.96,0:08:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,足够让人感动了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.28,0:08:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐 真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.00,0:08:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我们和亚美利亚舰队
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.40,0:08:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,上下夹击Capital军
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.08,0:08:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,逼其就范的这纸作战
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.21,0:08:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,相当于半张停战协议了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.77,0:08:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,亚美利亚的尼肯宁总统
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.39,0:09:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,已经允许我们移住Capital特区
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.37,0:09:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,这是在和谈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.44,0:09:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,按道理是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.52,0:09:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,但亚美利亚握有神轿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.70,0:09:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,过早谈判会陷入不利
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.50,0:09:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,等我为洛克帕报仇以后
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.00,0:09:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,再停战不迟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.66,0:09:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,还在说这个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.10,0:09:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,前往拉特尔派森号
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.19,0:09:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.37,0:09:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我们控制着弦月船和神轿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.65,0:09:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,处于绝对优势
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.00,0:09:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么发出停战协议！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.32,0:09:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我们和德瑞特舰队
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.10,0:09:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,之所以联手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.89,0:09:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,是为对付Capital舰队
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.91,0:09:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,他们经历过残酷的宇宙世纪战争
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.50,0:09:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,不可轻易相信
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.97,0:09:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,火蝾螈号
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.45,0:09:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,已经涂装耐热涂层
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.53,0:09:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,去地球也能赢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.74,0:09:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,知道么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.08,0:10:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,德瑞特舰队也在休整
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.74,0:10:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,「等降落地球后」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.03,0:10:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,他们也会这么想
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.50,0:10:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,降落地球后？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.25,0:10:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,站在德瑞特舰队的立场？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.32,0:10:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,到时会发生什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.44,0:10:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,自己好好想想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.93,0:10:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,少年
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.57,0:10:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.21,0:10:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,让开让开
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.45,0:10:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,这里已经是军事基地了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.52,0:10:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.08,0:10:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,请在这边的房间歇息
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.28,0:10:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,连第二站点Hayyan也要被军事化吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.98,0:10:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,请谅解
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.05,0:10:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,为将这里作为最终防线
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.19,0:10:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,此番让您成为神轿的人质
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.00,0:10:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,难为您了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.50,0:10:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,不算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.35,0:10:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是一直留在房间中而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.33,0:10:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.31,0:10:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你们这样！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.53,0:10:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,能保护茹甘司令吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.45,0:10:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 上校！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.73,0:10:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.72,0:10:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,看得入神了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.15,0:10:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs45}不许带进司令部
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.81,0:10:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs45}那放在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.55,0:10:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs45}美术品放在其他房间
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.87,0:11:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,上校
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.74,0:11:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,法皇安全抵达了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.26,0:11:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,司令为何亲自出击？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.09,0:11:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,据说德瑞特和古匈的舰队
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.78,0:11:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,正打算会合
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.53,0:11:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我要亲眼确认
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.13,0:11:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我们手中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.35,0:11:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,有直指亚美利亚总统的导弹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.08,0:11:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,面具还争取到满月船的协助
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.03,0:11:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.24,0:11:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,了解战争的临场感
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.22,0:11:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,有助指挥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.30,0:11:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,德瑞特舰队绝不敢动Capital塔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.38,0:11:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,可是 这些好战的地球人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.28,0:11:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,无药可救！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.01,0:11:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,德瑞特和亚美利亚舰队号称要会合
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.92,0:11:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,亚美利亚握有神轿和弦月船
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.10,0:11:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我不信古匈甘愿和德瑞特联手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.54,0:11:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,满月船上的面具上尉还没…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.53,0:11:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是去看出好戏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.20,0:11:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,布鲁金 出发
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,==================== Part B ====================
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.10,0:12:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,第二站点的Hayyan
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.62,0:12:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,驶出了Capital军的战舰？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.98,0:12:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,可能有这种事？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.42,0:12:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,公主殿下 贝鲁利
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.07,0:12:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我们之前看到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.60,0:12:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,布鲁金号在做出击准备吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.63,0:12:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,贝鲁妈妈为什么不阻止他们？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.27,0:12:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不妨碍冠艇时刻表
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.38,0:12:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,她是不会对军队说三道四的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.09,0:12:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,艾达小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.43,0:12:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,测试裙甲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.37,0:12:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.65,0:12:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,请吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.83,0:12:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,记得做激光校准
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.69,0:12:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.77,0:12:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,贝鲁利
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.71,0:12:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,能拖动强袭背包吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.63,0:13:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,不会用到的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.61,0:13:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.63,0:13:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,远距离狙击
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.80,0:13:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,只会杀驾驶员
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.95,0:13:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,贝鲁利
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.97,0:13:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.04,0:13:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.85,0:13:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,根据战局
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.29,0:13:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,选择有效的武器吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.50,0:13:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,好…好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.95,0:13:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,卡希尔上尉的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.87,0:13:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.25,0:13:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.87,0:13:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不过 贝鲁利学员
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.33,0:13:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,单纯的牵制攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.58,0:13:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,也是强袭的强项
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.71,0:13:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,总而言之
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.76,0:13:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,保护大家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.86,0:13:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,用G-Self的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.97,0:13:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.05,0:13:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,用舰桥监视器
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.58,0:13:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,观察敌人舰队
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.26,0:13:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,好认真
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.70,0:13:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.56,0:13:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.70,0:13:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,漂出船外会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.21,0:13:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,终于打起精神了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.51,0:13:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.31,0:13:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,雷达瘫痪了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.54,0:13:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,切换成CG
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.01,0:14:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,舰队会合的空域出现米诺夫斯基粒子？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.17,0:14:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,德瑞特和亚美利亚的舰队
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.40,0:14:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不是说达成停战协议了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.34,0:14:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,是这么期待的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.54,0:14:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,就算是CG化的缘故…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.29,0:14:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,两支舰队的动向
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.71,0:14:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,非常奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.14,0:14:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,这…不是对话的姿态！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.04,0:14:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,史堤厄 引擎临界
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.56,0:14:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,无线电瘫痪说明
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.44,0:14:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,这么近距离
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.43,0:14:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,会打舰队战！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.45,0:14:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,开火 让他们开火！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.07,0:14:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,现在炮击的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.32,0:14:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,会击落己方机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.47,0:14:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,亚美利亚舰队也迟迟不动
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.24,0:14:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,说明米诺夫斯基粒子是第三者所为
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.65,0:14:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,第三者？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.09,0:14:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,第三者在哪儿？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.76,0:14:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,是满月船方向吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.73,0:14:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不 太远
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.70,0:14:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,准备舰队战
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.01,0:14:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,机动战士后撤
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.16,0:14:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,满月船上有什么东西起飞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.76,0:14:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,面具那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.25,0:15:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,米克回防火蝾螈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.17,0:15:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.29,0:15:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,天才克里姆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.62,0:15:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,如何解读当前事态？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.13,0:15:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,不如观战！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.62,0:15:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,布鲁金放出了机动部队？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.95,0:15:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,最大倍率
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.62,0:15:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Capital军…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.42,0:15:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,看热闹不嫌事大
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.84,0:15:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,全员 一级战备待命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.12,0:15:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,磨磨蹭蹭会变成机动战士战
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.83,0:15:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,软体光束 照射准备
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.85,0:15:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,进入一级战斗距离
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.16,0:15:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,开始空转
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.57,0:15:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,启动
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.77,0:15:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yggdrasil 开眼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.63,0:15:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,踹开那丫头 被面具讨厌虽然不好受
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.85,0:15:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,总好过被认为是无能的女人！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.66,0:15:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yggdrasil 为我占卜运势
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.77,0:15:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,德瑞特和亚美利亚舰队悉数到场
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.77,0:15:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,真笨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.38,0:16:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,现在才发现
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.62,0:16:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,哪里来的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.42,0:16:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.08,0:16:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,满月船的机体
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.58,0:16:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,规避运动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.19,0:16:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,向目标开火
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.68,0:16:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,别被弯曲的光束迷惑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.88,0:16:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,右舷上方 上方！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.18,0:16:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,光束扭曲不同寻常
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.42,0:16:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,消失的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.55,0:16:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,像颗大树
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.56,0:16:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,是满月船带来的兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.01,0:16:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,软体光束的威力 这里也能感受到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.89,0:16:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,还不是全部
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.79,0:16:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,面具上尉的部下 芭拉拉·佩欧茹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.67,0:16:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,挺有一手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.22,0:16:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 是位出色的驾驶员
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.17,0:16:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,芭拉拉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.36,0:17:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,把嫉妒带上战场会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.88,0:17:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,看不见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.61,0:17:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,和葛兰登已经相隔大气层了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.67,0:17:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,看不见的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.75,0:17:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.12,0:17:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yggdrasil的威力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.21,0:17:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,加上奇亚队长和昆达拉的志向
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.84,0:17:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,一定能营造出不需要金星殖民圈的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.51,0:17:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然叫满月船
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.33,0:17:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,它其实只是艘运输舰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.38,0:17:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,这震动是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.92,0:17:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,相位…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.67,0:17:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,反转了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.35,0:17:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,这不就是软体光束的缺点么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.84,0:17:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,后退 舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.67,0:17:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,敌人近在眼前 为什么不反击？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.10,0:17:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,用强袭攻击乱向光束的源头
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.40,0:17:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,在此之前别去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.13,0:17:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.05,0:17:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,瞄准打
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.04,0:17:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.69,0:18:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我也在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.03,0:18:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,正中！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.88,0:18:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,噢！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.70,0:18:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.05,0:18:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,面具
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.17,0:18:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我作为驾驶员是完美的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.91,0:18:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,拿我和那种丫头相比
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.74,0:18:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,就杀了她
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.10,0:18:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,角度再深
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.41,0:18:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,要逃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.71,0:18:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,被埋伏 还遇到那种光束
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.00,0:18:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,诺顿将军的几内比绍号呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.44,0:18:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,眼下要逃！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.42,0:18:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,洛克帕告诉我的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.33,0:18:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,诶？这种时候还…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.01,0:18:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,地球方向援军
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.60,0:18:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,光束和导弹？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.42,0:18:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,护罩无法坚持
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.92,0:18:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,软体光束
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.98,0:18:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.69,0:18:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,这是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.92,0:18:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,是他来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.57,0:18:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,阻止震动
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.62,0:18:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,重启护罩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.46,0:18:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,光束也是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.03,0:18:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐 裙甲激光可以作为防护罩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.52,0:18:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,知道用法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.86,0:18:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Lucifer？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.11,0:19:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Lucifer打开突破口
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.44,0:19:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.76,0:19:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,拉莱雅小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.86,0:19:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Lucifer的那个姿势…啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.61,0:19:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.25,0:19:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,释放发振
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.32,0:19:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,放出
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.90,0:19:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,只要冲进怀里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.50,0:19:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.38,0:19:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,软体光束
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.59,0:19:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,全装裙甲是很亮的！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.87,0:19:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,软体光束被冲散了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.06,0:19:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,能用的穿梭机和小艇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.01,0:19:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,全部载人潜入Capital塔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.22,0:19:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,这是临阵脱逃！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.94,0:19:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,舰队的最终目的是回归作战！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.23,0:19:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,让尽可能多的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.75,0:19:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,从Capital塔潜入地球
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.55,0:19:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,求变于未来！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.61,0:19:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,您说求变…？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.83,0:19:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,去到地球愿望会脱胎换骨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.19,0:19:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,全员…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.14,0:19:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Capita…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.10,0:20:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,几内比绍号被击沉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.01,0:20:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,看见了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.57,0:20:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐去保护拉特尔派森上的父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.71,0:20:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.16,0:20:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,强袭模式
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.09,0:20:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,中弹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.88,0:20:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.79,0:20:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Self？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.99,0:20:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,光束被挡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.06,0:20:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Self的话 Yggdrasil！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.51,0:20:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Copy-Paste盾 能行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.89,0:20:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,摧毁整整一支舰队
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.05,0:20:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,意味着什么 明白吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.09,0:20:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,贝鲁利么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.45,0:20:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,芭拉拉·佩欧茹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.55,0:20:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,父亲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.73,0:20:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,请穿上太空服
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.37,0:21:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,金字塔的敌人呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.31,0:21:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,正在制服
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.91,0:21:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.91,0:21:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.10,0:21:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,父亲？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.18,0:21:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.70,0:21:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,这是…什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.12,0:21:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐 离开空域
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.44,0:21:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,碎片太多
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.03,0:21:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,到处是德瑞特和亚美利亚的残部
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.35,0:21:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.30,0:21:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,这片碎片带正在向满月船靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.08,0:21:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,靠近 靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.28,0:21:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,艾达小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.50,0:21:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,是…是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.67,0:21:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐 要哭的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.26,0:21:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,回去再哭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.71,0:22:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,父亲他…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.24,0:22:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,真的相信着停战
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.40,0:22:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,复原出那种东西的金星殖民圈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.93,0:22:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,面具和那里的满月船会合
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.21,0:22:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,拿出了那种兵器
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,==================== YOKOKU ====================
Comment: 0,0:23:59.27,0:24:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,无暇安慰失去父亲的姐姐
Comment: 0,0:24:02.52,0:24:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,突入大气层
Comment: 0,0:24:05.44,0:24:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,下集 G之复国
Comment: 0,0:24:07.44,0:24:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,跨越生死线
Comment: 0,0:24:08.99,0:24:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,电池不会耗尽！
